{"lastModified":1775541275090,"uri":"c::7646090758::vessel::fefa77f0-5b0f-11f0-be72-efba1d533dd2","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Montenegro, Croatia\n\nMORNING STAR is a 30-meter Ferretti Custom Line 100, combining Italian elegance, performance, and comfort. She accommodates up to 10 guests in 5 beautifully designed cabins, including a full-beam master on the main deck. The bright and spacious salon with large windows offers stunning panoramic views and connects seamlessly to the aft deck. Guests can enjoy sunbeds, and a lounge area on the sun deck — perfect for relaxing or entertaining. With a cruising speed of 20 knots and stabilizers at anchor, MORNING STAR ensures a smooth and pleasant journey. She is equipped with a variety of water toys and a fast tender for on-the-water fun. The interior is stylish and contemporary, ideal for both families and groups of friends. Whether cruising or at anchor, MORNING STAR is all about enjoying life at sea in style.","blueprint":{"name":"MORNING STAR","images":["/media/media::image::c::7646090758::vessel::fefa77f0-5b0f-11f0-be72-efba1d533dd2::assets::94e954d0-7f31-11f0-957b-b39f0ed51369/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7646090758::vessel::fefa77f0-5b0f-11f0-be72-efba1d533dd2::assets::94e8dfa0-7f31-11f0-957b-b39f0ed51369/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7646090758::vessel::fefa77f0-5b0f-11f0-be72-efba1d533dd2::assets::94eb77b0-7f31-11f0-957b-b39f0ed51369/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7646090758::vessel::fefa77f0-5b0f-11f0-be72-efba1d533dd2::assets::94e7a720-7f31-11f0-957b-b39f0ed51369/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7646090758::vessel::fefa77f0-5b0f-11f0-be72-efba1d533dd2::assets::94eb77b0-7f31-11f0-856d-4f489ef17bc4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7646090758::vessel::fefa77f0-5b0f-11f0-be72-efba1d533dd2::assets::94e62081-7f31-11f0-856d-4f489ef17bc4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7646090758::vessel::fefa77f0-5b0f-11f0-be72-efba1d533dd2::assets::94ebc5d